auctionCallback.t.sol
├─ when the caller is not the Auction contract
│  └─ it should revert
└─ when the call is the auction contract
   ├─ when the auction contract's caller is not the auction bidder contract
   │  └─ it should revert
   └─ when the auction contract's caller is the auction bidder contract
      └─ when the callback data is empty
         └─ it should revert
